  "body": "This issue has been observed on a Full node as well as an Archive node.\r\n\r\nThere seems to be an issue with Block processing once cleaning of peers happens. We solved this issue by increasing the number of peers to 1000 , and left it running for a day and then reconfigured the number of peers back to 300. The node seems to be running again smoothly.\r\n",
